      <h2><strong>Melanie Brown</strong></h2>
      <h5>'Scary Spice'</h5>
      <p> Mel B, was born Melanie Janine Brown in West Yorkshire, England on May 29, 1975. Mel was nicknamed 'Scary Spice.' She is a singer, songwriter, author and actress. In addition to being a member of Spice Girls, Mel has released solo albums. She has been married and divorced twice, to actor Jimmy Gulzar (1998-2000) and film producer Stephen Belafonte (2007-2017). She has 3 daughters, Angel Iris Murphy Brown, Phoenix Chi Gulzar, and Madison Brown Belafonte. </p>
    </section>




