      <h2><strong>Melanie Chisholm</strong></h2>
      <h5>'Sporty Spice'</h5>
        <p> Melanie C, was born Melanie Jane Chisholm in Lancashire, England on January 12, 1974. She was nicknamed 'Sporty Spice.' She is a songwriter, singer, entrepreneur and actress. In addition to being in the Spice Girls, she has sold over 20 million solo albums. She began her solo career in 1998. She has been dating Joe Marshall since 2014. She has one daughter, Scarlet Starr.</p>
    </section>

